| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1220 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d9c4e02e-b4c5-5b48-8842-ed1a6ec52560"
